{"id": "5233", "post": "<div class=\"post-5233 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-italy tag-milan tag-prometeus-net tag-xen tag-xenpower\" id=\"post-5233\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/xenpower-15-99quarter-1gb200gb-and-20-05quarter-2gb400gb-xen-vps-in-milan-italy/\" rel=\"bookmark\">XenPower \u2013 $15.99/quarter 1GB/200GB and $20.05/quarter 2GB/400GB Xen VPS in Milan, Italy</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/italy/\" rel=\"tag\">italy</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/milan/\" rel=\"tag\">milan</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/prometeus-net/\" rel=\"tag\">Prometeus.net</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/xen/\" rel=\"tag\">xen</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/xenpower/\" rel=\"tag\">xenpower</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> May 28, 2014 @ 1:00 am, by Maarten Kossen</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p>Salvatore, from <a href=\"http://www.prometeus.net\">Prometeus</a>, is back with some awesome new products for this XenPower brand! XenPower offers high-resource servers for a very reasonable price. This time, they are offering server with a lot of disk space, which are perfect to function as backup servers. XenPower was started because Salvatore once purchased the domain (xenpower.com) and still hadn\u2019t done anything with it. What better to do with it than offer some great Xen servers! These servers are hosted on a host node with dual Intel E5-2620v2 CPUs, 192GB of RAM and 12x 4TB SATA hard drives in RAID6! RAID6 is a little bit slower than RAID10 but allows for more disk space to be used, hence the competitive pricing on these offers. XenPower happens to be Prometeus\u2019 first deployment of servers with SATA disks (all others are SAS, SSD, or SAN) and I have to say, the speed is very good! We all know Prometeus: most reviews are very positive, support is fast, and the customer always comes first! Please share your own experiences with XenPower in the comments!</p><p><strong>The offers</strong><a href=\"http://www.xenpower.com\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/XenPower_-_2014-05-27_06.33.57-300x188.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/XenPower_-_2014-05-27_06.33.57-300x188.png.webp\" alt=\"XenPower_-_2014-05-27_06.33.57\" width=\"300\" height=\"188\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></a></p><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>XP-L</strong><p></p><ul><li>1 CPU core</li><li>1GB RAM</li><li>200GB disk space</li><li>2TB Bandwidth</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4 address</li><li>2x IPv6 address</li><li>XenPV/SolusVM</li><li>$15.99/quarter ($5.33/month)</li><li><a href=\"https://www.prometeus.net/billing/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=120\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td><strong>XP-XL</strong><p></p><ul><li>2 CPU cores</li><li>2GB RAM</li><li>400GB disk space</li><li>4TB Bandwidth</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4 address</li><li>2x IPv6 address</li><li>XenPV/SolusVM</li><li>$20.05/quarter ($6.68/month)</li><li><a href=\"https://www.prometeus.net/billing/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=121\">Order here</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span id=\"more-5233\"></span></p><p>Prometeus accepts payments via Paypal. VAT, at 22%, is added if you\u2019re an EU citizen/company without a valid VAT ID. Prometeus is a registered LIR (RIPE NCC member), which means they own their IP addresses. Like noted above, an IPv6 /64 is available for free on request. No refunds are offered. For more information, have a read of their <a href=\"http://www.prometeus.net/sito/term-of-service\">Terms of Service</a>.</p><p><strong>Network information</strong></p><p>Looking glass Milan: <a href=\"http://lg-milano.prometeus.net/\">http://lg-milano.prometeus.net/</a></p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fxenpower-15-99quarter-1gb200gb-and-20-05quarter-2gb400gb-xen-vps-in-milan-italy%2F&amp;t=XenPower%20-%20%2415.99%2Fquarter%201GB%2F200GB%20and%20%2420.05%2Fquarter%202GB%2F400GB%20Xen%20VPS%20in%20Milan%2C%20Italy\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=XenPower%20-%20%2415.99%2Fquarter%201GB%2F200GB%20and%20%2420.05%2Fquarter%202GB%2F400GB%20Xen%20VPS%20in%20Milan%2C%20Italy&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fxenpower-15-99quarter-1gb200gb-and-20-05quarter-2gb400gb-xen-vps-in-milan-italy%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fxenpower-15-99quarter-1gb200gb-and-20-05quarter-2gb400gb-xen-vps-in-milan-italy%2F&amp;title=XenPower%20-%20%2415.99%2Fquarter%201GB%2F200GB%20and%20%2420.05%2Fquarter%202GB%2F400GB%20